events.name: Singapore OpenStack Meetup
events.description: Hello Stackers Hoping you will be able to join us for an SG OpenStack meetup.   Agenda for Meetup - OpenStack - Docker Containers and Atomic host- Openshift - CloudForms (manageIQ) Q & A ,General discussion on Emerging technologies & next Meetup directions  during pizza / drinks break . If you would like to speak/present on any aspect of OpenStack or would like to share real world examples with best practices, challenges, etc please let us know.  All welcome!! * IF there is any change in place i will let you know in advance Thanks To Redhat for sponsoring it !!!
events.location: 8 Shenton Way, #10-00 AXA Tower, Red Hat Asia Pacific Pte Ltd, Singapore

More details about open space :  http://www.openspaceworld.org/files/tmnfiles/2pageos.htm Refreshment & pizza at 7:00 PM  Topic generating at 7:30 PM Discussions at 08:00 PM Address : Barclays  - Marina bay financial centre tower 2 10 marina Boulevard , 23rd floor.  Please report at reception.
